
WordPress Python Library

============================================================================

A simple python library for WordPress XML-RPC interface.
At the time are supported this methods:

* getUsersBlogs
* getUserInfo
* getPost
* getRecentPosts
* newPost
* editPost
* deletePost
* newMediaObject
* getCategoryList
* getPostCategories
* setPostCategories
* getTrackbackPings
* publishPost
* getPingbacks

See example.py for simple example script
